definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be patient, to have patience"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bind, to tie, to fetter, to shackle"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to persevere, to endure"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to refrain, to abstain, to renounce"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to ask to be patient, to admonish to be patient"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to console, to comfort"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to conserve"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to preserve, to can"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of صَبَرَ (ṣabara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fettering, shackling"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"patience, forbearance","examples":[{"text":"الصَّبْرُ مِفْتَاحُ ٱلْفَرَجِ","english":"Patience is the key to deliverance."},{"text":"قَلَّ صَبْرُهُ.","english":"His patience ran out."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"composure, self-control"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"equanimity, steadfastness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"perseverance, endurance, hardiness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ice","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"aloe"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bitterness; juice of any bitter plant, aloe, myrrh","tags":["Classical"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to ballast"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Aramaic, found in Jewish Palestinian Aramaic צברה and Classical Syriac ܨܒܪܐ (ṣabrā, ṣabbārā), ܨܘܪܐ (ṣawrā), from Akkadian [script needed] (ṣibaru, ṣiburu, “a pointed gardening instrument; a fleshy excrescence; a plant in medical texts a medication for gall-bladder disease, apparently aloe comparable to the garden-tool by its lanceolate leaves”). For relevant vocalization variants, against the standard Arabic صَبِر (ṣabir, “aloe”) and صَبْر (ṣabr, “aloe”), the Andalusi dialect, which has been reckoned the most conservative of the Middle Arabic ones, used صِبْر (ṣibr) and صِبَر (ṣibar), and صَبَّار (ṣabbār), صُبَّار (ṣubbār, “cactus; nonstandardly and also Andalusi aloe”) is extended from this word.\n\nDenominal verb of صَابُورَة (ṣābūra, “ballast”)."},"ipa":["/sˤa.ba.ra/","/sˤab.ba.ra/","/sˤabr/","/sˤa.bar/","/sˤa.bir/"]}